{"tid":542042,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(視后) 唐詩詠與影帝任達華合演英皇新片","createTime":"2018-01-27T05:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T08:25:40.000Z","uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3b4f6224a911332eb46487d6708862172a1b7595","tid":542042,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T05:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.facebook.com/discussofdrama/posts/1168884669912541\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fdiscussofdrama%2Fposts%2F1168884669912541&d=Z4SfTW0YYMIcWAN5R97USo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=97a3f612\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.facebook.com/discussofdrama/posts/1168884669912541</a><br />\n<br />\n由劉嘉玲、任達華及唐詩詠等主演，葉念琛執導的英皇賀歲喜劇《我的情敵女婿》將於2月15日上映，剛榮獲視后的唐詩詠，在戲中一改劇集《不懂撒嬌的女人》Cherry的苦情形象，飾演劏房大王任達華的得力助手，面對挑剔嚴厲的惡魔老闆，詩詠總有辦法滿足華哥的要求，展現機智幽默。詩詠初拍賀歲片立即傳來喜訊，榮登視后寶座，導演葉念琛第一時間致電道賀，她感謝葉導演的信任。"},{"pid":"f19f19e5d02bfb1f2cd6f092c866e2f673104c52","tid":542042,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T06:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d88288dc2d5ead6f8b8d036196adf5b787db58","tid":542042,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T08:19:00.000Z","msg":"又拍埋啲垃圾"},{"pid":"f2d29faee60212927211ad4eefb800eed9235a77","tid":542042,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8d88288dc2d5ead6f8b8d036196adf5b787db58","tid":542042,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T08:19:00.000Z","msg":"又拍埋啲垃圾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T08:25:40.000Z","msg":"劉嘉玲、任達華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}